<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Young_Earth_creationism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Websites critical of YEC">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Websites critical of YEC</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.toarchive.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.toarchive.org/" rel="nofollow">The TalkOrigins Archive</a></li>
